item.description:
The Best year end party and an incredibly inexepensive evening. Aerochix the fantastic tribute to Aerosmith and HRT profiled on Good Morning America and Chronicle are the entertainment and an great buffet dinner served by S&S restaurant Cambridge. A cash bar is arranged and plenty of door prizes contest and fun. Dont miss this great holiday evening and be sure to take a photo with Santa and his sexy elves on hand for your holiday entertainment.
Buy tickets now at http://cwcaoyearendparty.eventbrite.com/ from $20.00
